-grief-age-older-parent-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20miscarriages%3C%2Fa%3E)%20but%20my%20first%20after%20completing%20a%20nutrition%20course%20from%20Stanford%20Medicine.%20I%20always%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20health%20and%20fitness%2C%20but%20this%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20even%20more%20empowered%20with%20knowledge%20about%20how%20to%20eat%20healthy%20during%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20it%20all%20went%20out%20the%20window%20because%20I%20was%20so%20sick%20during%20the%20first%20trimester.%20It%20was%20absolute%20survival%20mode.%20I%20was%20vomiting%20a%20lot%20and%20going%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%20because%20I%20was%20so%20dehydrated.%20I%20gave%20myself%20permission%20to%20eat%20anything%20that%20I%20could%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20was%20a%20burger%20or%20chicken%20nuggets%20from%20McDonald's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20a%20lot%20better%20now%20that%20I'm%20approaching%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-had-a-3rd-trimester-abortion-because-of-brain-abnormalities-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethird%20trimester%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20I%20understand%20that%20even%20with%20the%20best-laid%20plans%2C%20life%20sometimes%20gets%20in%20the%20way.%20You%20have%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20roll%20with%20those%20punches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211722304-fd98-4d55-8d34-5b75a7647ee9%5C%22%3EI%20focus%20on%20healthy%20foods%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20make%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20eat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-volume-high-fiber-foods-lose-fat-keep-muscle-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplenty%20of%20filling%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20flavor%20each%20day.%20One%20of%20my%20favorite%20tricks%20is%20using%20salsa%20to%20add%20flavor%20to%20dishes.%20Another%20secret%20weapon%20of%20mine%20is%20sriracha.%20Even%20during%20pregnancy%2C%20the%20more%20spice%2C%20the%20better%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I'm%20health-conscious%2C%20I'm%20also%20tired.%20Not%20only%20am%20I%20pregnant%20at%2042%2C%20but%20I'm%20chasing%20after%20my%20two%20other%20children%2C%20who%20are%205%20and%206.%20Cooking%20and%20cleaning%20feels%20like%20a%20chore%2C%20so%20I%20rely%20on%20batch%20meals%20when%20I%20can.%20I%20cook%20large%20pots%20of%20turkey%20chili%20and%20roast%20huge%20batches%20of%20vegetables%20that%20I%20can%20eat%20for%20the%20next%20two%20or%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22645%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Melissa%20Pfeister%20smiling%20and%20staring%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664cbaea9fc063e829b34189%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22484%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMelissa%20Pfeister%20is%20a%20nutritionist.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Melissa%20Pfeister%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269112e6a-fe99-45ca-83d5-db55b2270944%5C%22%3EBreakfast%20is%20typically%20eggs%20or%20oatmeal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMornings%20are%20busy%2C%20so%20I%20always%20make%20a%20breakfast%20that%20the%20kids%20will%20eat%2C%20too.%20Usually%2C%20that's%20something%20like%20eggs%20or%20oatmeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20eating%20eggs%2C%20I'll%20combine%202-3%20egg%20whites%20with%20one%20whole%20egg%20to%20load%20up%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fhigh-protein-snacks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplenty%20of%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20love%20to%20eat%20that%20with%20whole-wheat%20bread%20or%20an%20herb%20tortilla%20wrap%20to%20add%20fiber.%20If%20I'm%20having%20a%20wrap%2C%20I%20pack%20it%20with%20tons%20of%20arugula%20to%20get%20my%20greens%20and%20vitamins%20in%20and%20top%20it%20with%20spicy%20sriracha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20favorite%20is%20plain%20oats%20flavored%20with%20almond%20butter%2C%20unsweetened%20almond%20milk%2C%20and%20cinnamon.%20I%20pack%20that%20with%20fruit%