Duvauchelle%20and%20her%20partner%20Ipo%20married%20in%20Hawaii%20and%20now%20plan%20weddings%20on%20the%20island.%3Cp%3EMahina%20Choy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOver%20half%20the%20weddings%20in%20Hawaii%20in%202023%20were%20destination%20weddings%20between%20non-resident%20couples.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Hawaiian%20wedding%20planner%20from%C2%A0O'ahu%20shares%20what%20couples%20should%20know%20before%20booking%20their%20wedding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECouples%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20high%20costs%2C%20varying%20microclimates%20and%20to%20support%20local%20vendors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20wedding%20season%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20decisions%20to%20make%20about%20the%20theme%2C%20guest%20list%20size%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20location.%20In%202023%2C%2062%25%20of%20weddings%20in%20Hawaii%20were%20between%20non-residents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.hawaii.gov%2Fvitalstatistics%2Fpreliminary-non-resident-marriage-data-total-and-same-sex%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20preliminary%20government%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20state%20is%20a%20popular%20destination%20wedding%20spot%20for%20its%20luscious%20greenery%2C%20picturesque%20views%2C%20and%20beautiful%20weather%2C%20but%20how%20do%20you%20decide%20if%20it's%20right%20for%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20married%20in%20Hawaii%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20in%20most%20American%20states.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fidelity.com%2Flearning-center%2Fsmart-money%2Faverage-wedding-cost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20wedding%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Hawaii%20in%202023%20was%20%2428%2C000.%20The%20cheapest%20US%20state%20to%20get%20married%20in%20is%20Alaska%2C%20with%20an%20average%20cost%20of%20%2412%2C083.%20Hawaiian%20weddings%20are%20more%20costly%20because%20anything%20not%20produced%20or%20grown%20in%20Hawaii%20must%20be%20shipped%20in%2C%20raising%20the%20prices%20of%20flowers%2C%20food%2C%20and%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tell%20my%20clients%20to%20look%20at%20the%20average%20price%20of%20weddings%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20L.A.%20because%20those%20are%20more%20similar%20in%20price%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Zabrina%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20owner%20of%20queer-owned%20wedding%20and%20event%20planning%20business%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thegayagenda.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Gay%20Agenda%20Collective%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20worked%20with%20dozens%20of%20couples%20to%20plan%20weddings%20and%20events%20in%20their%20home%20in%20O'ahu%20and%20beyond%2C%20and%20she%20has%20a%20few%20tips%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20for%20couples%20considering%20having%20their%20nuptials%20on%20the%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c6fc982-b6e3-412f-88cb-ced7bcbfc840%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20clear%20on%20why%20you%20want%20to%20get%20married%20in%20Hawaii%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20when%20deciding%20to%20get%20married%20in%20Hawaii%20is%20to%20educate%20yourself%20about%20the%20state's%20history%20and%20understand%20why%20it%20would%20be%20meaningful%20to%20get%20married%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20first%20questions%20to%20ask%20yourself%20is%2C%20'Why%20Hawaii%3F'%26quot%3B%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20familial%20connection%20or%20fell%20in%20love%20here%2C%20that's%20great.%20That%20reason%20will%20guide%20you%20in%20the%20process%20of%20planning%20your%20wedding%20in%20an%20intentional%20way%2C%20which%20starts%20with%20connecting%20back%20to%20the%20local%20land%20and%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZablan-Duvauchelle%20encouraged%20couples%20to%20think%20about%20ways%20to%20give%20back%20to%20the%20island%2C%20whether%20by%20having%20guests%20donate%20to%20local%20organizations%20in%20lieu%20of%20gifts%2C%20sharing%20a%20list%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkanakaeconomy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20businesses%20that%20guests%20can%20support%20during%20their%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kanuhawaii.org%2Fneeds%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaving%20a%20volunteering%20day%20with%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc7e2fd4-c6df-430e-9b07-8bbfe07d0cdc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20local%20vendors%20whenever%20possible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wedding%20industry%20is%20incredibly%20lucrative%2C%20and%20a%20huge%20economic%20boost%20for%20Hawaii.%20Couples%20should%20honor%20this%20and%20support%20local%20vendors%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20said%20couples%20can%20find%20local%20photographers%20and%20wedding%20planners%2C%20as%20well%20as%20buy%20guest%20favors%20from%20local%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20local%20wedding%20planner%20can%20help%20you%20identify%20local%20vendors%2C%26quot%3B%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20also%20use%20social%20media%20to%20find%20vendors%20that%20align%20with%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f9b9db3-afd1-4e7b-8a0a-34563024bf66%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChoose%20a%20venue%20space%20that%20makes%20sense%20for%20you%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20weather%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawaiimagazine.com%2Fhawaii-has-10-of-the-worlds-14-climate-zones-an-explorers-guide-to-each-of-them%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHawaii%20has%20many%20microclimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20consider.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Waikiki%20side%20of%20O'ahu%20and%20Poipu%20to%20Waimea%20on%20Kauai%20tend%20to%20be%20drier%20than%20the%20mountains%20and%20valleys%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20island.%20Rain%20is%20always%20possible%20regardless%20of%20where%20you%20are%2C%20so%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20encourages%20couples%20to%20plan%20and%20budget%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you're%20at%20a%20venue%20that's%20really%20green%2C%20know%20that%20it's%20usually%20a%20product%20of%20rain%2C%26quot%3B%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Hawaii%2C%20every%20day%20could%20be%20the%20rainy%20season%20with%20the%20most%20rain%20from%20November%20to%20April%2C%20so%20you'll%20want%20to%20factor%20a%20tent%20into%20your%20budget%20or%20look%20for%20a%20venue%20that%20has%20a%20contingency%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fseagrant.soest.hawaii.edu%2Fcoastal-access-in-hawaii%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20private%20beaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Hawaii.%20According%20to%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%2C%20locals%20and%20visitors%20alike%20may%20be%20passing%20by%20and%20enjoying%20the%20shoreline.%20She%20added%20that%20couples%20should%20check%20local%20laws%20before%20choosing%20a%20specific%20beach%20because%20most%20have%20restrictions%20and%20require%20a%20permit%20for%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planner%20said%20couples%20wanting%20a%20more%20private%20waterfront%20should%20look%20for%20secluded%20beaches%20with%20harder-to-reach%20access%20points%2C%20estates%2C%20or%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c27c3b6-8f61-4535-a4b2-37019e06be34%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStart%20planning%20early%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPlanning%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20is%20true%20for%20all%20weddings%2C%20especially%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20according%20to%20Zablan-Duvauchelle.%20Many%20popular%20and%20high-profile%20venues%20in%20Hawaii%20can%20book%20out%20a%20year%20in%20advance%2C%20with%20weekend%20dates%20often%20filling%20up%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20specifc%20special%20date%20in%20mind%2C%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20encourages%20you%20to%20book%20your%20venue%20no%20later%20than%2015%20months%20in%20advance%20to%20help%20guarantee%20your%20spot.%20Choosing%20a%20venue%20can%20also%20be%20a%20helpful%20exercise%20in%20selecting%20a%20final%20guest%20count%20since%20some%20venues%20have%20much%20lower%20capacities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20start%20booking%20your%20preferred%20vendors%20seven%20to%20twelve%20months%20in%20advance.%20They%20will%20use%20your%20wedding%20date%20to%20confirm%20their%20availability%20and%20any%20travel%20costs%20that%20may%20be%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20your%20vendors%20for%20hair%20and%20makeup%20trials%20or%20catering%20tastings%2C%20Zablan-Duvachelle%20suggests%20booking%20a%20wedding%20planning%20trip%20to%20help%20guide%20your%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef44a3e3-9458-451c-b090-015629eeb43a%5C%22%3EIt's%20the%20small%20things%20that%20count%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20where%20you%20decide%20to%20have%20your%20wedding%2C%20Zablan-Duvauchelle%20said%20the%20details%20make%20a%20wedding%20sing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20her%20couples%20request%20personalized%20touches%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5PBaWxvBJg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseating%20charts%20made%20of%20friendship%20bracelets%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5wj79FP18V%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3D-printed%20centerpieces%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20small%20things%20make%20a%20wedding%20feel%20unique%20to%20the%20couple%20and%20are%20as%20important%20as%20the%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-planning-hawaii-wedding-costs-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716375905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664dcbd320abc1efe8fc4352%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-planning-hawaii-wedding-costs-2