%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hype%20behind%20Nvidia's%20chips%20is%20no%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Huang%20stood%20onstage%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20for%20an%20event%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BWoodstock%20of%20AI%26quot%3B%20(he%20seemed%20to%20prefer%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-taylor-swift-nod-shows-aware-of-tech-reputation-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomparisons%20to%20Taylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E)%20as%20the%20world%20awaited%20the%20reveal%20of%20Nvidia's%20next-generation%20chips%2C%20or%20GPUs%2C%20dubbed%20Blackwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackwell%20offers%20technological%20leaps%20over%20its%20predecessor%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20H100%20GPU%20that%20tech%20CEOs%20such%20as%20Zuckerberg%20have%20been%20actively%20seeking%20to%20stockpile%20%E2%80%94%20that%20have%20been%20talked%20up%20in%20the%20industry%20since%20its%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20Blackwell%20would%20be%20twice%20as%20powerful%2C%20making%20it%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-gpu-targets-1-8-million-ai-chips-this-year-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobvious%20purchase%20for%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20to%20build%20bigger%2C%20smarter%2C%20more%20efficient%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20competitors%20have%20been%20busy%20developing%20AI%20chips%20of%20their%20own%20to%20reduce%20reliance%20on%20Nvidia's%20increasingly%20expensive%20offerings.%20Price%20estimates%20for%20the%20most%20powerful%20Blackwell%20chip%2C%20the%20GB200%2C%20are%20about%20%2470%2C000%20each%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20double%20the%20price%20of%20an%20H100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flisa-su-amd-billionaire-jensen-huang-nvidia-cousin-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAMD%20CEO%20Lisa%20Su%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who's%20Huang's%20cousin%2C%20is%20aiming%20to%20pry%20Nvidia%20customers%20aw