ef_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20a%20PTI%20report%2C%20the%20city%20spends%20Rs%20200%20crore%20annually%20on%20waste%20management.%C2%A0A%20total%20of%20850%20vehicles%20crisscross%20the%20city%20daily%20and%20collect%20692%20tonnes%20of%20wet%2C%20683%20tonnes%20of%20dry%20and%20179%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%2C%20an%20official%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20video%2C%20many%20praised%20the%20city's%20culture%20and%20its%20people%20who%20know%20their%20duties%20and%20prioritize%20cleanliness.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Cleanliness%20and%20order%20are%20not%20matters%20of%20mere%20taste%20and%20upbringing%2C%20they%20are%20among%20the%20essential%20requirements%20of%20human%20beings.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20commented%2C%20''India%20would%20look%20very%20different%20if%20more%20cities%20had%20residents%20like%20those%20in%20Indore%20who%20prioritize%20cleanliness.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20user%20said%2C%20''If%20this%20were%20to%20be%20replicated%20throughout%20the%20country%20then%20India%20would%20be%20the%20cleanest%20place%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Sir.%20Thanks%20for%20sharing%20such%20wonderful%20videos%20and%20awakening%20the%20people.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20Indore%20model%20is%20the%20best%20model%20of%20a%20smart%20city%20and%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Indori%20people%20take%20it%20personally%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20cleanliness%2C%20they%20make%20sure%20as%20visitors%20as%20well%2C%20we%20don't%20litter%2C%20my%20family%20there%20guided%20us%20not%20to%20litter%20on%20the%20road%20and%20stopped%20the%20car%20for%20putting%20waste%20in%20the%20bin%2C''%20stated%20a%20fourth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716374520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F455us058_indore_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwatch-us-vlogger-impress