deos%2C%20Chennai-based%20Irfan%20shared%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20travelled%20to%20Dubai%20to%20get%20a%20gender%20determination%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20vlogger%2C%20who%20has%204.29%20million%20followers%20on%20YouTube%2C%20revealed%20the%20child's%20gender%20in%20one%20of%20the%20videos.%20Along%20with%20footage%20of%20the%20examination%2C%20he%20revealed%20what%20the%20doctor%20had%20told%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gender%20reveal%20video%20received%20nearly%202%20million%20views%2C%20while%20the%20Dubai%20trip%20vlog%20garnered%20over%201%20million%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevealing%20the%20gender%20of%20an%20unborn%20child%20is%20illegal%20in%20India%20and%20punishable%20under%20the%20PCPNDT%20Act%20(Pre%20Conception%20%26amp%3B%20Pre%20Natal%20Diagnostic%20Techniques%20Act).%20The%20Act%20is%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20gender-based%20abortions%20and%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20and%20rights%20of%20unborn%20children.%20It%20was%20enacted%20in%201994%20to%20prevent%20female%20foeticide%20and%20address%20the%20declining%20sex%20ratio%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Health%20Department%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20him%20under%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20from%20the%20Health%20Department%20says%20Irfan%20also%20posted%20videos%20of%20a%20family%20event%20in%20which%20the%20foetus'%20gender%20was%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20bid%20to%20take%20legal%20action%2C%20the%20enforcement%20officer%20has%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20Mr%20Irfan.%20Actions%20like%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20decline%20in%20birth%20of%20girl%20babies%20not%20just%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20but%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20department%20has%20also%20written%20to%20the%20Cyber%20wing%20of%20the%20police%20to%20remove%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YouTuber%20said%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20down%20the%20video%20and%20will%20reply%20to%20the%20notice%20once%20he%20receives%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20couple%20was%20met%20with%20congratulations%20from%20many%2C%20it%20also%20sparked%20criticism%2C%20with%20some%20suggesting%20it%20could%20inadvertently%20promote%20the%20practice%20of%20traveling%20abroad%20to%20determine%20the%20sex%20of%20a%20baby.%20Others%20went%20further%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20might%20be%20a%20calculated%20move%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20subscribers%2C%20views%2C%20and%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20stringent%20measures%20against%20unauthorized%20ultrasound%20centers%20have%20significantly%20curbed%20this%20practice%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20noticeable%20improvement%20in%20India's%20sex%20ratio.%20According%20to%20data%20presented%20by%20the%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20in%20Parliament%20last%20year%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%2C%20which%20stood%20at%20876%20female%20babies%20per%201000%20male%20babies%20in%202005%2C%20has%20risen%20to%20907%20between%202018%20and%202020.%20States%20like%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20been%20commended%20for%20their%20proactive%20measures.%20Notably%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20seen%20a%20remarkable%20improvement%20in%20its%20sex%20ratio%2C%20climbing%20from%20918%20in%202015%20to%20942%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716370620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F46suasq_tamil-youtuber-irfan_625x300_22_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpopular-food-vlogger-gets-notice-for-revealing-gender-of-unborn-child-5719799%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20popular%20YouTuber%20has%20landed%20in%20trouble%20for%20sharing%20the%20gender%20of%20his%20unborn%20child%20on%20social%20media%20after%20getting%20sex%20determination%20test%20overseas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F