used%20by%20it%20and%20cracked%20jokes%2C%20others%20highlighted%20the%20negative%20impacts%20of%20such%20a%20culture%20and%20called%20it%20a%20''sad%20state%20of%20affairs.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Could%20have%20been%20done%20on%20the%20phone%20-%20both%20-%20the%20meeting%20and%20the%20shoe%20shopping.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20commented%2C%20''This%20woman%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20companies%20are%20asking%20employees%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20office%20and%20abolish%20WFH%20policies.%20The%20problem%20is%2C%20attending%20a%20meeting%20without%20being%20present%20in%20it%20100%25%20is%20as%20good%20as%20not%20attending%20it%20at%20all..''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20user%20said%2C%20''These%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20people%20who%20made%20companies%20rescind%20Work%20From%20Home%20policies.%20Such%20a%20sad%20state.%20it%20creates%20an%20impression%20that%20people%20in%20India%20have%20no%20work%20ethics.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''My%20only%20thought%20is%20someone%20should%20introduce%20them%20to%20this%20unique%20invention%20called%20Bluetooth%20headphones%2C''%20joked%20a%20fourth.%20A%20fifth%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Deciding%20which%20shoe%20to%20throw%20at%20organizer%20of%20such%20useless%20meetings.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Either%20she%20is%20practising%20the%20art%20of%20'putting%20the%20best%20foot%20forward'%20or%20trying%20out%20'putting%20oneself%20in%20someone%20else's%20shoes'%20while%20being%20in%20a%20corporate%20setting%2C''%20stated%20another.%20''A%20heel-larious%20solution%20for%20work-life%20balance%2C''%20joked%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%2C%20an%20X%20user%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fpic-of-bengaluru-man-working-on-laptop-in-theatre-reignites-work-life-balance-debate-5340161%5C%22%3Eworking%20on%20a%20laptop%20inside%20a%20movie%20hall.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0A%20video%20of%20a%20man%20attending%20a%