-road-rage-on-cctv-child-inside-bengaluru-scooterist-shatters-car-window-5719853%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-road-rage-road-rage-on-cctv-child-inside-bengaluru-scooterist-shatters-car-window-5719853%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-road-rage-road-rage-on-cctv-child-inside-bengaluru-scooterist-shatters-car-window-5719853%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20Indian-Born%20Nikesh%20Arora%2C%20Second-Highest%20Paid%20CEO%20In%20The%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndian-born%20Nikesh%20Arora%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%2C%20has%20landed%20the%20second%20spot%20on%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal's%202023%20list%20of%20highest-paid%20CEOs%20in%20the%20US.%20With%20a%20compensation%20of%20%24151.43%20million%2C%20the%2056-year-old's%20earnings%20have%20surpassed%20those%20of%20many%20tech%20giants%2C%20like%20Meta's%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Google's%20Sundar%20Pichai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20some%20facts%20about%20Nikesh%20Arora%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.iitbhufoundation.org%2Fmr-nikesh-arora-ece-89%2F%5C%22%3ENikesh%20Arora%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20born%20on%20February%209%2C%201968%2C%20in%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20His%20father%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20He%20studied%20at%20The%20Air%20Force%20School%20(Subroto%20Park)%20before%20graduating%20in%20Electrical%20Engineering%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(BHU)%20Varanasi%20in%201989.%20After%20a%20brief%20stint%20at%20Wipro%2C%20he%20went%20to%20the%20US%20for%20an%20MBA%20at%20Northeastern%20University%20in%20Boston%2C%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHis%20work%20journey%20started%20in%201992%20when%20he%20joined%20Fidelity%20Investments%2C%20where%20he%20took%20on%20roles%20in%20finance%20and%20technology%20management.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20became%20the%20Vice%20President%20of%20Fidelity%20Technologies.%20In%202000%2C%20he%20established%20T-Motion%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Deutsche%20Telekom%2C%20which%20later%20became%20part%20of%20T-Mobile's%20core%20services.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Marketing%20Officer%20of%20the%20T-Mobile%20International%20Division%20of%20Deutsche%20Telekom%20AG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202004%2C%20Nikesh%20Arora%20joined%20Google.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalindian.com%2Fprofiles%2Fnikesh-arora%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Eheld%20major%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20Vice%20President%20of%20Europe%20operations%2C%20President%20of%20Europe%2C%20Middle%20East%20and%20Africa%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20and%20Chief%20Business%20Officer.%20He%20worked%20at%20Google%20for%20almost%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Arora%20then%20worked%20for%20Japan's%20SoftBank%20Corp%20in%202014.%20He%20became%20Vice%20Chairman%20of%20the%20group%20and%20CEO%20of%20SoftBank%20Internet%20and%20Media%20Inc.%20He%20was%20expected%20to%20succeed%20SoftBank's%20CEO%2C%20Masayoshi%20Son%2C%20and%20received%20%24208%20million%20in%20compensation%20over%20two%20years.%20However%2C%20in%20June%202016%2C%20he%20surprised%20everyone%20by%20resigning%20from%20his%20roles%20at%20SoftBank.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20join%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%20in%202018%20and%20is%20now%20their%20CEO%20and%20Chairman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202015%2C%20Nikesh%20Arora%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Global%20Indian%20award%20at%20the%20ET%20Corporate%20Excellence%20Awards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716368880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fllo4272g_nikesh-arora_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-nikesh-arora-indian-born-ceo-who-is-second-highest-paid-in-the-us-5719679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikesh%20Arora%20studied%20at%20The%20Air%20Force%20School%20before%20earning%20an%20Electrical%20Engineering%20degree%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(BHU)%20Varanasi%20in%201989.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-nikesh-arora-indian-born-ceo-who-is-second-highest-paid-in-the-us-5719679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-nikesh-arora-indian-born-ceo-who-is-second-highest-paid-in-the-us-5719679%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-nikesh-arora-indian-born-ceo-who-is-second-highest-paid-in-the-us-5719679%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Beyond%20ignorant'%3A%20Man%20filmed%20'body%20slamming'%20orca%20in%20New%20Zealand%20is%20fined%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716368400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-orca-new-zealand_6562397.jpg%3F20240522090439%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbeyond-ignorant-man-filmed-body-slamming-orca-in-new-zealand-is-fined-13141109%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2050-year-old%20man%20has%20been%20caught%20on%20camera%20jumping%20off%20a%20pleasure%20boat%20to%20try%20and%20%26quot%3Bbody%20slam%26quot%3B%20an%20orca%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20in%20what%20was%20branded%20%26quot%3Bdisgraceful%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpathetic%26quot%3B%20behaviour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%