anic%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganic%20farming%20is%20not%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20what%20Ganesh%20realised%20when%20he%20began%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20subject%20around%202002.%20But%20even%20so%2C%20as%20he%20weighed%20the%20long-term%20fruits%20(pun%20intended)%20of%20organic%20techniques%20with%20the%20allures%20of%20chemical%20farming%2C%20he%20knew%20the%20former%20held%20more%20promise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201978%20my%20father%20had%20planted%201%2C000%20mango%20saplings%20on%20the%20land.%20He%20did%20this%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Ratnagiri%20was%20experiencing%20a%20harsh%20climate%2C%20less%20rainfall%2C%20undeveloped%20roads%20and%20power%20cuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20watching%20his%20father%20climbing%20to%20heights%20sometimes%2C%20to%20water%20the%20trees%20when%20the%20rain%20gods%20weren%E2%80%99t%20being%20kind.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20he%20persisted%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%2C%20adding%20that%20the%201%2C000%20trees%20flourished.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%20my%20father%20in%20farming%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant%20another%201%2C000%20mango%20saplings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20have%20over%202%2C000%20mango%20trees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20the%20farm%20always%20had%20an%20audience.%20People%20were%20intrigued%20at%20how%20the%20father-son%20duo%20had%20created%20a%20yellow%20oasis%2C%20and%20the%20organic%20methods%20they%20had%20used%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20many%20guests%20who%20wanted%20to%20observe%20how%20we%20were%20preparing%20our%20organic%20fertilisers%20from%20cow%20dung%20(we%20had%2035%20cows%20in%20our%20shed)%2C%20how%20we%20used%20neem%20to%20make%20our%20pestici