0homestay%2C%20sometimes%20as%20a%20side%20dish%2C%20other%20times%20as%20the%20hero%20ingredient.%20%3Cem%3EAamti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20spicy%2C%20sweet%20and%20sour%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20pickles%2C%20%3Cem%3Epanna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20cooling%20Indian%20summer%20drink%20made%20with%20unripe%20green%20mangoes)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eaamras%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20milky%20drink%20made%20with%20mango%20pulp)%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efresh%20fruit%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20some%20of%20the%20delights%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Ganesh%2C%20he%20maintains%20that%20diving%20into%20agro-tourism%20was%20the%20best%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CAgrotourism%20is%20beneficial%20because%20you%20get%20direct%20customers%20for%20your%20products.%20These%20are%20connections%20that%20you%20make%20for%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-1_11zon-1715947790.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%20plenty%20of%20activities%20for%20guests%20to%20partake%20in%20at%20the%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay.%20These%20include%20birdwatching%2C%20boating%2C%20mango%20canning%20and%20more%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-1_11zon-1715947790.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-1_11zon-1715947790-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-1_11zon-1715947790-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2F